data.description: Welcome home to this beautifully appointed four-bedroom, 2.5-bath colonial offers a perfect blend of style and functionality. From the moment you step through the front door, you'll be captivated by the open concept living room and kitchen area. The newer laminate flooring (2020) and wood accent wall create a warm and inviting atmosphere, complemented by a beautiful stone fireplace (2021). The lovely eat-in kitchen features a center island, prep space, ample cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and a stylish backsplash. The dining space with a slider leading to the private fenced backyard makes it ideal for both indoor and outdoor entertaining. The backyard, enclosed by a privacy fence installed in 2018, also boasts a new deck added in 2023. The first floor is completed with a convenient half bath, making it perfect for guests. As you head upstairs, you'll find four spacious bedrooms. The master suite featuring an en-suite bath and a walk-in closet. Three additional bedrooms provide ample space for family or guests, and a full bath conveniently serves these rooms. The laundry room on this level adds to the practicality of the home. The lower level offers potential for additional recreational space, making it a versatile area that can be tailored to your needs. Whether you choose to finish it for added living space or utilize it for storage, the lower level enhances the overall functionality of the home. This property is move-in ready, showcasing both modern style and practical design. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful house your new home. Call today to schedule a private viewing and experience the charm and comfort this property has to offer.
